data.description: 3 bed 1 bath ranch home, 1116 sqft with full walk out basement, sitting on 31.52 acres with 22 acres of private forest management land, last select cut was done in 2020. Fireplace with insert in main living, with baseboard heat, as well as a potbelly and open fireplace in the basement. Enjoy views from a wrap around deck and screened porch. Several alternative building sites. Home sits at approx 3100 ft in elevation with the top of the property at approx 3500 ft. Lot of active hunting land with plenty of deer and turkey, and a few bear and bobcats on property.
